==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unsaddle
<hw>Un*sad"dle</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>saddle</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>To strip of a saddle; to take the saddle from, as a
horse.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To throw from the saddle; to unhorse.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unsadness</ent>⟦br⟧
